.0, whose performance is close to the state of the art.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 23 Jan 2021 21:11:29 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 24 Feb 2021 19:51:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-26"}
