 result of this work is that we have been able to\ncharacterize the above mentioned energy levels of a DBEC in a complex trapping\npotential.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 24 Jan 2021 15:11:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-11"}
